items.name: The Angry Birds Movie
items.longDescription: In this hilarious animated adventure comedy, you'll finally find out why the birds are so angry. In an island paradise populated entirely by happy, flightless birds _ or almost entirely, Red, a bird with a temper problem, speedy Chuck, and the volatile Bomb have always been outsiders. But when the island is visited by mysterious green piggies, it's up to these unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to. Featurettes Include: "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Action Music!", "In-Theater Policy Trailers A Gift Card For Chuck", "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Pig's Theme", "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Red's Theme", "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Red's Anger Theme", "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Mission Theme", "Making Music with Composer Heitor Pereira Chuck's Theme"; Photo Gallery; Blake Shelton "Friends" Music Video. Languages: English, French, Spanish, Portuguese and Korean.

items.name: Sony Gold Wireless Stereo Headset (PS4)
items.shortDescription: The Sony Gold Wireless Stereo Headset (PS4) delivers amazing depth and audio clarity, elevating your gaming experience with customizable modes created by developers exclusively for PlayStation. High fidelity 7.1 virtual surround sound breathes new life into the urban jungles and alien worlds you explore, while the hidden noise cancelling microphone makes it easy to connect with your friends and teammates. When you're on the move, use your Sony Gold wireless headset with your favorite mobile device via the included 3.5mm audio cable or fold it up into its travel pouch until the next round. This is how games were made to sound.
items.longDescription: <p><br><b>Sony Gold Wireless Stereo Headset (PS4):</b></p><ul><li>A Headset for Gamers: Experience everything from the big booms to whisper-quiet warnings in stunning 7.1 virtual surround sound and chat with friends through the hidden noise cancelling microphone on this PlayStation wireless headset</li><li>Developed by PlayStation: With the Headset Companion App, download custom game modes created exclusively for PlayStation by developers that are specifically tuned to enhance the audio in your favorite games.</li><li>Stylish Comfort: Slip into comfort you can enjoy for hours and a look you can take anywhere with this Sony Gold wireless headset. Further customize your look by swapping out the removable faceplates for something more your style</li><li>Adaptable Audio: Connect wirelessly to your PS4, PS3, and home computer, or connect to your PS Vita system or other mobile device with the included 3.5mm audio cable and take your sound with you</li><li>Also in the Sony Gold Wireless Stereo Headset (PS4) Box:<ul><li>Wireless Adaptor</li><li>3.5mm Audio Cable</li><li>Micro-USB Recharging Cable</li><li>Travel Pouch for PlayStation wireless headset</li></ul></li></ul>

items.name: 3M WorkTunes Hearing Protector, MP3 Compatible with AM/FM Tuner
items.shortDescription: This 3M TEKK Protection Digital Worktunes Hearing Protector 90541-80025T is designed with innovation and functionality, providing all-in-one hearing protection and entertainment. It helps with noises at 85 decibels or more. This superior hearing protection unit will help you focus on your projects and not on your safety products. This is an ideal choice for the workshop, job site, yard work or to give as a gift. The 3M hearing protector with voice assist features AM/FM radio reception with digital tuning and a convenient LCD display. It is scanner, MP3 and iPod compatible. The Voice Assist feature makes it easy to use. The AM/FM stereo radio hearing protector uses Bass Boost technology for enhanced sound quality and performance. Strong construction and durable materials help prevent breakage and stand up to daily use. It is lightweight and comfortable to wear all day long. It has soft foam ear cushions for comfort.
items.longDescription: The 3M TEKK Protection Digital Worktunes Hearing Protector 90541-80025T is ideal for your personal and professional use. You can easily see and hear your favorite station or song while protecting your delicate hearing with digital tuning, a convenient LCD display and innovative dB limiter.<br><b>3M TEKK Protection Digital WorkTunes Hearing Protector and AM/FM Stereo Radio with Voice Assist, 90541-80025T:</b><br><ul><li>3M hearing protector with voice assist features Voice Assist for easier use</li><li>Bass Boost technology for enhanced sound quality and performance</li><li>Strong construction and durable materials help prevent breakage and better withstand daily use</li><li>Soft ear padding for extended comfort</li></ul>
